    "## Pengenalan Data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Dataset yang dipakai diambil dari kaggle. Dataset ini adalah data sales dari suatu perusahaan supermarket selama 3 bulan dan dari 3 cabang pada 2019. \n",
    "\n",
    "Dateset ini terdiri dari Invoice Id, Total sales, sampai Rating yang diberikan customers:\n",
    "\\\n",
    "\\\n",
    "\\\n",
    "Berikut ini adalah informasi mengenai kolom yang ada di dataset yang saya ambil dari halaman kaggle datasetnya:\n",
    "\n",
    "Invoice id: Computer generated sales slip invoice identification number\n",
    "\n",
    "Branch: Branch of supercenter (3 branches are available identified by A, B and C).\n",
    "\n",
    "City: Location of supercenters\n",
    "\n",
    "Customer type: Type of customers, recorded by Members for customers using member card and Normal for without member card.\n",
    "\n",
    "Gender: Gender type of customer\n",
    "\n",
    "Product line: General item categorization groups - Electronic accessories, Fashion accessories, Food and beverages, Health and beauty, Home and lifestyle, Sports and travel\n",
    "\n",
    "Unit price: Price of each product in $\n",
    "\n",
    "Quantity: Number of products purchased by customer\n",
    "\n",
    "Tax: 5% tax fee for customer buying\n",
    "\n",
    "Total: Total price including tax\n",
    "\n",
    "Date: Date of purchase (Record available from January 2019 to March 2019)\n",
    "\n",
    "Time: Purchase time (10am to 9pm)\n",
    "\n",
    "Payment: Payment used by customer for purchase (3 methods are available â€“ Cash, Credit card and Ewallet)\n",
    "\n",
    "COGS: Cost of goods sold\n",
    "\n",
    "Gross margin percentage: Gross margin percentage\n",
    "\n",
    "Gross income: Gross income\n",
    "\n",
    "Rating: Customer stratification rating on their overall shopping experience (On a scale of 1 to 10)"
   ]
  },

   ]

   "source": [
    "## Topik Permasalahan"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Perilaku customer Supermarket selama 3 bulan terakhir"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## SMART dan Problem Statement"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "SMART :\n",
    "\n",
    "S : Mencari tahu perilaku customer Supermarket dari rating, produk yang dibeli, dan jam berbelanja. \\\n",
    "M : Rating lebih dari 6 \\\n",
    "A : Mengukur kepuasan customer dari segi rating, dan mencari tahu perilaku customer dari kategori produk yang sering dibeli, jam berbelanja, dan alat pembayaran mereka. \\\n",
    "R : Mengetahui perilaku customer untuk mengembangkan Supermarket atau layanan Supermarket. \\\n",
    "T : Mengukur perilaku customer selama 3 bulan terakhir, dan bisa dibagi menjadi perhari atau perjam."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Problem Statement : \n",
    "\n",
    "Mengetahui perilaku customer Supermarket dalam 3 bulan terakhir untuk meningkatkan pelayanan dan sales, melalui kapan mereka berbelanja, produk apa saja yang mereka suka, mereka lebih suka membayar dengan apa, dan bagaimana rating mereka terhadap Supermarket."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Penjabaran dan Objectives"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Penjabaran:\n",
    "1. Kapan saja Supermarket ramai? Bisa berdasarkan jam, hari, dll. (Visual)\n",
    "2. Apakah secara keseluruhan rating Supermarket bagus? (Statistics Descriptive)\n",
    "3. Seperti apa pilihan customer Supermarket untuk membayar pembelian mereka? (Visual)\n",
    "4. Apa saja produk yang disukai oleh customer Supermarket? (Visual)\n",
    "5. Apakah pria dan wanita memiliki kesukaan yang berbeda terhadap produk di Supermarket? (Visual)\n",
    "6. Apakah customer yang memiliki membership memiliki perilaku yang berbeda dengan yang tidak punya? (Visual)\n",
    "7. Apakah customer pria dan wanita memiliki jam berberlanja di Supermarket tersendiri? (Statistics Inferential)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Objectives:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Mengetahui keramaian Supermarket\n",
    "2. Mengetahu rata-rata rating Supermarket\n",
    "3. Mengetahui preference alat pembayaran yang dipakai customer\n",
    "4. Mengetahui category product yang sering dibeli\n",
    "5. Mengetahui preference wanita dan pria terhadap product category\n",
    "6. Mengetahui apakah customer memiliki member berperilaku berbeda dengan yang tidak\n",
    "7. Mengetahui apakah jam berbelanja customer pria dan wanita berbeda.\n"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "# Using Mann Whitney U to get to know whether time of female and male is different\n",
    "t_test , p_value = st.mannwhitneyu(time_male, time_female)\n",
    "print('Statistics=%.3f, p_value=%.3f' % (t_test , p_value))\n",
    "\n",
    "alpha = 0.05\n",
    "if p_value > alpha:\n",
    " print(\"Waktu berbelanja customer wanita sama dengan waktu berbelanja customer pria (fail to reject H0)\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    " print(\"Waktu berbelanja customer wanita berbeda dengan waktu berbelanja customer pria (reject H0 or accept H1)\")"
   ]
